---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import { LINKS } from '../../lib/constants';
---

<DocsLayout
	title="Introduction"
	description="GetCookie is a community recognition bot for Discord. Give Cookies to members, earn crypto rewards, and build a culture of appreciation."
>
	<h1><img src="/logo.png" alt="GetCookie Logo" style="height: 1.2em; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;" /> What is GetCookie?</h1>
	<p class="lead">
		GetCookie is a community recognition bot for Discord that makes appreciation fun and meaningful.
		Members reward each other with reactions and cookies — a playful way to celebrate contributions, climb the leaderboards, and build a culture of appreciation in your community or organization.
	</p>

	<h2>Key Features</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Community Recognition</strong> — Members reward each other with Cookies and by emoji reactions</li>
		<li><strong>Leaderboards</strong> — Celebrate top contributors and see who's making the biggest impact</li>
		<li><strong>Build Culture</strong> — Reinforce the values that make your community thrive</li>
		<li><strong>Get Rewards</strong> — Cookies are real crypto tokens that can be redeemed for rewards</li>
		<li><strong>Engagement Tracking</strong> — Track engagement trends and what drives your community</li>
	</ul>

